{"tid":121113,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你受夠你部垃撚圾電腦未？！","createTime":"2017-02-15T03:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T06:48:41.000Z","uid":81176,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d772b933556d4a8df94bfee9bc482ec924fd4a46","tid":121113,"uid":81176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我相信好多扮工巴絲都對公司既電腦都十分不滿，<br />\n<br />\n常見例子包括:<br />\n<br />\nE.g.1  你老闆俾部淨係用到excel嘅電腦designer用;<br />\nE.g. 2  你老闆要CS做online livechat但部電腦連上網都有問題<br />\nE.g. 3  你老闆叫員工用試用版/老翻office<br />\n<br />\n有d直頭精彩到係乜柒都連load唔撚到呀!!<br />\n利申: 我公司部電腦廢到連用excel都hang機<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我決定搞個&quot;全港大中小蚊型企換新電腦大行動&rdquo; !<br />\n目標係推到你老闆見到,推到你老闆內疚,推到你老闆悔改 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望可以集合眾巴絲既力量，一齊用念力屌死你老闆呢個on9仔! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 強烈要求有關部門做野!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8e15e67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8e15e67.jpg&h=edb1362a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2twodaysoff/photos/a.873108712829277.1073741828.868836319923183/893593094114172/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2twodaysoff%2Fphotos%2Fa.873108712829277.1073741828.868836319923183%2F893593094114172%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=aceedaf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2twodaysoff/photos/a.873108712829277.1073741828.868836319923183/893593094114172/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e9556e5931165eca086c573f629f11d575b92163","tid":121113,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"做生意唔是咁做的"},{"pid":"81a5b740a3120c4b5603c04264499dee17406305","tid":121113,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"其實換隻SSD 已經好快"},{"pid":"30dadbc42cb32d64d0ac1